  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, cook until onion is translucent.",
    "Add curry powder, cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add bhuna sauce, stir to combine.",
    "Add fideo pasta, stir to coat with sauce.",
    "Pour in coconut milk, bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low, let cook for 15-20 minutes or until pasta is al dente.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, and scotch bonnet pepper (if using).",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro or scallions (optional)."
